{
  "stem": "1208.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The smell was so horrendous and the idea of it, it demoralized all of us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I had not seen Bernard Hillman then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But one day, when I came to work and a detail was marching back to camp, and I thought there was someone in there that resembled him.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But he didn't have his uniform on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was so emaciated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was him though.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because he saw me and he lagged behind one day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he said, this is the end.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when he first met me, he had said to me, what do you remember most about your home?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had told him about my father singing arias from operas, but vividly the lilac tree.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The lilac tree that reached up to my parents' bedroom.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on my mother's birthday, on May 8th, my father would stand-- it was very romantic-- under the tree and sing, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Think you can translate that?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said to me, if we live, I want to marry you and I will a plant you a lilac tree.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[CRYING]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Plaszow he said to me, I don't think I'll ever plant that lilac tree now because I can't live.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't go on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I cannot go on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I wrote him a little note and had it smuggled to him that he may feel he could release himself from that promise, but I hadn't released him yet.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No way could he do that to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A promise is a promise.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so I see throughout as I wrote this down, I realized how we supported one another.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Not with food alone-- with thought, with strength, to hold out and hold out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Not that that would have prevented the Nazis from doing away with us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it was also chancy.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
